        SORRY_I_DON_T_HAVE_ANYTHING_TO_SELL                                     = 7615,  -- Sorry, I don't have anything to sell you. I'm trying to start a business selling goods from Gustaberg, but it's not easy getting stuff from areas that aren't under Bastokan control.
        SORRY_I_DON_T_HAVE_ANYTHING_TO_SELL_2                                   = 7616,  -- Sorry, I don't have anything to sell you. I'm trying to start a business selling goods from Zulkheim, but it's not easy getting stuff from areas that aren't under Bastokan control.
        SORRY_I_DON_T_HAVE_ANYTHING_TO_SELL_3                                   = 7617,  -- Sorry, I don't have anything to sell you. I'm trying to start a business selling goods from Derfland, but it's not easy getting stuff from areas that aren't under Bastokan control.
        I_M_TRYING_TO_START_A_BUSINESS_SELLING                                  = 7618,  -- I'm trying to start a business selling goods from Kuzotz, but it's not easy getting stuff from areas that aren't under Bastokan control.
