        WELCOME_TO_THE_TROUPE_VALERIANO_VALERIANO_AT_YOUR                       = 7620,  -- Welcome to the Troupe Valeriano. Valeriano, at your service! Have a laugh, then spend some cash! Treats and sweets from exotic lands!
        YOU_GUYS_MUST_VE_WORKED_REAL_HARD_BASTOK                                = 7621,  -- You guys must've worked real hard. Bastok is a much nicer place now than when I left it. I wish I could go back to bashing monsters again, like in the old days.
        HOW_DO_YOU_LIKE_BASTOK_IT_S_MY                                          = 7622,  -- How do you like Bastok? It's my hometown, you know! Sure, there are still some...unsightly elements, but it's still the best city in the world!
        THE_MUSIC_STORE_HERE_SELLS_REALLY_GOOD_INSTRUMENTS                      = 7623,  -- The music store here sells really good instruments! Shh, don't tell the boss...but I'm gonna-wanna sneak off and go there later.
        THERE_ARE_PLENTY_OF_BARDS_AROUND_BUT_I                                  = 7624,  -- There are plenty of bards around, but I'm the best harpist in Vana'diel. You don't believe me? Then stay awhile and listen.
        THE_FOOD_HERE_S_TERRRIBLE_C_MON_WINDURRRSTIANS                          = 7625,  -- The food here's terrrible! C'mon, Windurrrstians, work harder! I miss Windurstian cuisine!
        LIKE_TO_SEE_MY_NEW_KNIFE_TRRRICK_GOOD                                   = 7626,  -- Like to see my new knife trrrick? Good, but keep your distance if you value your various extremities and bodily protrusions!
        THIS_PLACE_IS_TIRING                                                    = 7627,  -- This place...is tiring...
        I_M_A_MIME                                                              = 7628,  -- ... (I'm a mime.)
        DO_I_LIKE_AIRSHIPS_ARE_YOU_CRAZY_THEY                                   = 7629,  -- Do I like airships? Are you crazy!? They're a menace!
        I_HEAR_THAT_EVERY_TIME_AN_AIRSHIP_PASSES                                = 7630,  -- I hear that every time an airship passes overhead, a terrible beast appears and destroys everything!
        IT_S_TRUE_THE_MONSTER_WAS_SIGHTED_ON                                    = 7631,  -- It's true! The monster was sighted on the Rolanberry Fields! Please...I need to convince people that airships are dangerous. I need to get my hands on whatever that monster drops--that way, I can prove it to them!
        YOU_GOT_IT_MAGNIFICENT_BUT_WASN_T_THE                                   = 7632,  -- You got it! Magnificent! But wasn't the beast horrible, as I said it would be? There's no time to waste. Now that I have proof, I have to warn everyone about the airship menace!!!
        OH_AND_HERE_TAKE_THIS                                                   = 7633,  -- Oh, and here. Take this.
        OH_YOU_AGAIN_WHAT_AIRSHIPS_ARE_SCARY_WHAT                               = 7634,  -- Oh, you again. What? Airships are scary? What are you talking about? They're the most marvelous things on earth...er, I mean, in the sky.
        AIRSHIPS_BRING_THE_MOST_DELICIOUS_THINGS_I_VE                           = 7635,  -- Airships bring the most delicious things I've ever tasted! Remember the % you brought back? It was great!
        WHY_AM_I_HERE_TO_WATCH_THOSE_MAJESTIC                                   = 7636,  -- Why am I here? To watch those majestic airships cut through the clouds, of course!
        TAKE_MY_WORD_FOR_IT_HOUSEWORK_IS_NOT                                    = 7637,  -- Take my word for it, housework is not easy. Especially clearing clogged chimneys--that takes up a whole day!
        HMM_I_REMEMBER_MY_MOTHER_IN_LAW_TELLING                                 = 7638,  -- Hmm... I remember my mother-in-law telling me there was an item that cleared chimneys in a flash, but what was it, I wonder? Do you know?
        YES_CAN_I_HELP_YOU_YOU_HAVE_A                                           = 7639,  -- Yes, can I help you? You have a clogged chimney? I say, adventurers really do have a lot cut out for them, what with defeating monsters, and doing housework...
        YOU_NEED_PUT_SOME_IN_YOUR_CHIMNEY_AND                                   = 7640,  -- You need %. Put some in your chimney and light a fire, then boom! Your troubles are gone.
        I_KEEP_TELLING_MY_DAUGHTER_IN_LAW_ABOUT                                 = 7641,  -- I keep telling my daughter-in-law about it, but young people these days never listen to what their elders tell them.
        IS_THIS_IT_THIS_CAN_CLEAR_CHIMNEYS_MY                                   = 7642,  -- Is this it? This can clear chimneys? My mother-in-law said so?
        HMM_I_GUESS_I_FAINTLY_REMEMBER_HER_TALKING                              = 7643,  -- Hmm...I guess I faintly remember her talking about it. Oh well, as long as it works. Here's something for your trouble.
        AH_AN_ADVENTURER_AND_I_SEE_YOU_VE                                       = 7644,  -- Ah! An adventurer! And I see you've also earned your %! I need your help!
        YOU_SEE_THESE_WORDS_HAVE_BEEN_BOTHERING_ME                              = 7645,  -- You see, these words have been bothering me for some time: Under a full moon, toward the stars of Ifrit, a bird brings a letter to the ship in the sky.
        I_DON_T_REMEMBER_WHERE_I_HEARD_IT                                       = 7646,  -- I don't remember where I heard it. I woke up this morning with those words...and a whopping headache...as the only clues to where I was last night.
        COULD_YOU_TRY_FINDING_THIS_LETTER_FOR_ME                                = 7647,  -- Could you try finding this letter for me? I fancy it might be a clue that leads to great treasure! What? Yes, of course, I will give you a share!
        A_SHIP_THAT_FLIES_TOWARD_THE_STARS_OF                                   = 7648,  -- A ship that flies toward the stars of Ifrit? Interesting imagery, but I've written better prose in my sleep.
        AH_LET_ME_SEE_LET_ME_SEE_WHAT                                           = 7649,  -- Ah! Let me see! Let me see! What? It's just a wishy-washy love letter. What's it doing on an airship?
        HERE_TAKE_IT_BACK_IT_GIVES_ME_THE                                       = 7650,  -- Here, take it back. It gives me the creeps! Oh, and here's something for you. Now, go away!
