        THEY_SAY_THAT_WHEN_THE_SNOW_STOPS_FALLING                               = 7660,  -- They say that when the snow stops falling and the pond freezes, even the lightest piece of parchment sinks slowly to the bottom. I want you to put this, the testament of our pledge, in that pond.
