        WHERE_CAN_YOU_FIND_THEM_IF_YOU_RE                                       = 7687,  -- Where can you find them? If you're the kind of adventurer I think you are, you should have a pretty good idea. Just don't do anything I wouldn't...heh heh.
        INCREDIBLE_YOU_WERE_ABLE_TO_DEFEAT_BOTH_OF                              = 7688,  -- Incredible! You were able to defeat both of them!? Here's the % I promised. You deserve it. I can't wait to see the faces of the guys at Jeuno headquarters when they hear about you!
        THANK_YOU_VERY_MUCH_FOR_ALL_OF_YOUR                                     = 7689,  -- Thank you very much for all of your help.
        A_HERO_S_STORY_THE_DEEDS_OF_IN                                          = 7690,  -- %, a hero's story! The deeds of %, in all their gloryt
        A_TRAVELING_BARD_WALKS_FAR_AND_NEAR_WHILE                               = 7691,  -- A traveling bard walks far and near While wand'ring this celestial sphere From bustling towns to godforsaken lands. But none I love more than the swell Inhabitants of Vana'diel, Espec'lly when their gil comes to my hands.t
        PAY_ME_WHAT_YOU_THINK_I_M_WORTH                                         = 7692,  -- Pay me what you think I'm worth And songs of legend may spring forth.t
        OPEN_YOUR_EARS_AND_TAKE_A_RATION_OF                                     = 7693,  -- Open your ears and take a ration Of my melodic cantillation.t
