        THE_ESCALATION_IN_ACTIVITY_AROUND_NORG_ALSO_TROUBLES                    = 8381,  -- The escalation in activity around Norg also troubles me. Soon there will be airships going to the Outlands. Who knows what those adventurers will be up to when that starts?
        AH_AND_WHAT_ABOUT_THE_STEAMING_SHEEP_RESTAURANT                         = 8382,  -- Ah, and what about the Steaming Sheep Restaurant? That old place still doing fine? I mean...it's making money, right? There aren't any strange guys hanging around the proprietor...are there?
        SIR_I_STOP_IN_EVERY_DAY_AFTER_MY                                        = 8383,  -- Sir? I stop in every day after my duties are complete, and business seems decent as usual...
        GOOD_GOOD_FORGET_WHAT_I_SAID                                            = 8384,  -- Good...good. Forget what I said.
        I_WONDER_WHAT_S_WRONG_WITH_CHIEF_CID                                    = 8385,  -- I wonder what's wrong with Chief Cid.
        YOU_MEAN_YOU_HAVEN_T_HEARD_CID_S                                        = 8386,  -- You mean you haven't heard? Cid's got the hots for the lady at the tavern. Word has it that she's a widow...
        WOW_MAYBE_CHIEF_CID_S_GOT_A_SOFT                                        = 8387,  -- Wow. Maybe Chief Cid's got a soft spot after all.
        WELCOME_BACK_HOW_ARE_THE_ADVENTURERS_FARING                             = 8388,  -- Welcome back. How are the adventurers faring?
        LADY_AYAME_WHAT_BRINGS_YOU_TO_THIS_AREA                                 = 8389,  -- Lady Ayame! What brings you to this area?
        I_WAS_JUST_ON_MY_WAY_TO_ANOTHER                                         = 8390,  -- I was just on my way to another appointment and decided to stop by. What is the status of Port Bastok? Is everything all right?
        CHIEF_CID_ASKED_US_THE_SAME_QUESTION_EARLIER                            = 8391,  -- Chief Cid asked us the same question earlier... But there is nothing out of the ordinary, and Port Bastok is safe as long as we are here, Lady Ayame!
        VERY_WELL_THE_ONE_THING_THAT_CONCERNS_ME                                = 8392,  -- Very well. The one thing that concerns me, though, is the recent activity of the Tenshodo. Now that the airship will be making trips to the Outlands, I feel that they may team up with the pirates in Norg for another one of their get-rich-quick schemes.
        I_HAVE_HEARD_THAT_MILADY_CONDUCTED_HER_TRAINING                         = 8393,  -- I have heard that Milady conducted her training in Norg. I am grateful for this important piece of information. I will reinforce the number of guards I have patrolling the area.
        UNDERSTOOD_CARRY_ON                                                     = 8394,  -- Understood. Carry on.
        SIGH_SURELY_THERE_ISN_T_ANOTHER_WOMAN_AS                                = 8395,  -- <Sigh>... Surely there isn't another woman as beautiful as Lady Ayame. In the desert of Musketeers, she's a garden of roses. But I wonder why she was all the way out here.
