        HEY_HAVE_YOU_HEARD_OF_MY_SISTER_AYAME                                   = 8406,  -- Hey. Have you heard of my sister Ayame? She's a samurai and a member of the Mythril Musketeers. She's so cool. Me? I'm nothing compared to her...
