        AH_THANK_YOU_AGAIN_FOR_ALL_YOU_HAVE                                     = 8469,  -- Ah, %. Thank you again for all you have done for my daughter and me.
        I_M_GOING_TO_TAKE_GOOD_CARE_OF                                          = 8470,  -- I'm going to take good care of my mom's katana. I, too, will learn to be strong like her.
        I_REMEMBER_MY_SISTER_TALKING_ABOUT_HOW_THE                              = 8471,  -- I remember my sister talking about how the strongest warriors are the ones who draw their blades the least. I think I know what she was talking about now...
        A_MISTER_HANI_NOW_THAT_YOU_MENTION_IT                                   = 8472,  -- A Mister Hani? Now that you mention it, I do remember an adventurer going by that name... He was talking about a letter he received from some Galka.
        HOWEVER_HE_SEEMED_MORE_INTERESTED_IN_HIS_NEXT                           = 8473,  -- However, he seemed more interested in his next quest than that letter. He kept asking if I knew anything about the Palborough Mines.
        MY_LATE_HUSBAND_KNEW_MUCH_OF_THOSE_MINES                                = 8474,  -- My late husband knew much of those mines. When I told him the stories my husband had told me, the adventurer got excited and said he was setting off for the Mines the next day.
        AND_THAT_WAS_THE_LAST_I_HEARD_OF                                        = 8475,  -- And that was the last I heard of him. I hope nothing terrible has happened to him...
        WHAT_DO_YOU_MEAN_RYOMA_SENT_YOU_HE                                      = 8476,  -- What do you mean, Ryoma sent you? He wants to know about that old scroll we found nearly two decades ago?
        WHY_ME_RYOMA_KNOWS_I_DON_T_WANT                                         = 8477,  -- Why me? Ryoma knows I don't want to deal with that guy anymore...
        OH_WELL_LISTEN_UP_IT_ALL_STARTED_TWENTY                                 = 8478,  -- Oh well... Listen up. It all started twenty years ago...
        THIS_IS_WHAT_YOU_WERE_LOOKING_FOR_RIGHT                                 = 8479,  -- This is what you were looking for, right? Just where the ancient writings said it would be.
        DAMN_YOU_RE_GOOD_YOMI_HOW_DID_YOU                                       = 8480,  -- Damn, you're good, Yomi. How did you...
