        HAVE_YOU_FORGOTTEN_ALREADY_KAGETORA_I_TOLD_YOU                          = 8483,  -- Have you forgotten already, Kagetora? I told you before I left that this was going to be my last mission.
        BUT_YOU_WERE_KIDDING_RIGHT_YOU_CAN_T                                    = 8484,  -- But you were kidding, right? You can't leave us now.
        NO_I_WAS_NOT_KIDDING_IF_YOU_HAVE                                        = 8485,  -- No, I was not kidding. If you have any problems with my decision, you can take them up with Gilgamesh.
        HEY_WHAT_THE_HELL_ARE_YOU_DOING_HERE                                    = 8486,  -- Hey! What the hell are you doing here!?
        TO_THINK_THAT_A_WEASEL_LIKE_THAT_WOULD                                  = 8487,  -- To think that a weasel like that would end up with the hand of the most beautiful woman to ever set foot in Norg... Oh, sorry about that. I got side-tracked.
