        I_CAN_MAKE_A_QUIVER_OR_POUCH_FOR                                        = 8833,  -- I can make a quiver or pouch for up to seven sets of the same kind of ammunition. So you could bring me, say, one hundred ninety-eight % and two of those %, for example. I like to do things real efficient-like, you see, so make sure they're in multiples of ninety-nine.
