        HANDS_OVER_THE                                                          = 10016,  -- % hands over the %.
        I_WILL_GIVE_YOU_THIS_IN_ITS_PLACE                                       = 10017,  -- I will give you this in its place. If you ever go to Aht Urhgan, please stop by Salaheem's Sentinels.
        YOU_OBTAIN_3                                                            = 10018,  -- You obtain %.
        REMEMBER_TO_VISIT_SALAHEEM_S_SENTINELS_IN_AL                            = 10019,  -- Remember to visit Salaheem's Sentinels in Al Zahbi the next time you visit the Empire of Aht Urhgan!
        HELLO_WHEN_IT_COMES_TO_CELEBRATING_AND_FESTIVITIES                      = 10020,  -- Hello! When it comes to celebrating and festivities, I'm your moogle, kupo! Today I'm here on behalf of the M.H.M.U. to reward adventurers for their hard work in protecting our cities!
        GREETINGS_FROM_THE_MOG_HOUSE_MANAGEMENT_UNION_WHEN                      = 10021,  -- Greetings from the Mog House Management Union! When it comes to celebrating and festivities, I'm your moogle, kupo!
        I_DON_T_KNOW_WHAT_WE_D_DO                                               = 10022,  -- I don't know what we'd do without you... Keep it up, kupo!
        YOU_THERE_I_SUPPOSE_YOU_VE_HEARD_THE                                    = 10023,  -- You there. I suppose you've heard the gossip flying around town--the talk of ghosts?
        HAVE_YOU_HEARD_GHOSTS_YES_I_VE_HEARD                                    = 10024,  -- Have you heard? Ghosts!? Yes, I've heard.
        THEN_WE_MAY_MOVE_ON_TO_MORE_IMPORTANT                                   = 10025,  -- Then we may move on to more important matters.
        WOULD_YOU_BE_WILLING_TO_AID_ME_IN                                       = 10026,  -- Would you be willing to aid me in exorcising these spirits?
        SIGH_ALLOW_ME_TO_EXPLAIN_I_AM_AN                                        = 10027,  -- <Sigh>... Allow me to explain. I am an exorcist--a banisher of spirits.
        I_HAVE_TRAVELED_HERE_AT_THE_BEHEST_OF                                   = 10028,  -- I have traveled here at the behest of a certain personage from this nation who is well aware of my skill in such matters.
        THE_REQUEST_IS_FAIRLY_ROUTINE_I_AM_TO                                   = 10029,  -- The request is fairly routine--I am to banish the spirits that have suddenly appeared within the town. But there is a problem...
        THESE_GHOSTS_ARE_NOT_SIMPLE_APPARITIONS                                 = 10030,  -- These ghosts are not simple apparitions.
        WHEN_THEY_YET_LIVED_THEY_BELONGED_TO_A                                  = 10031,  -- When they yet lived, they belonged to a witch coven known as the Dark Lilies.
        AND_THEY_USE_THE_LANGUAGE_OF_SPIRITS_THE                                = 10032,  -- And they use the language of spirits--the Cursed Tongue. It is not a language I am familiar with.
        THE_ART_OF_THE_EXORCIST_INVOLVES_LEARNING_THE                           = 10033,  -- The art of the exorcist involves learning the mind of the spirit in order to bring it under control. I am at the point of capitulation.
        THAT_IS_WHY_I_AM_CALLING_ON_ADVENTURERS                                 = 10034,  -- That is why I am calling on adventurers to aid me.
        I_WANT_YOU_TO_DISGUISE_YOURSELF_AS_A                                    = 10035,  -- I want you to disguise yourself as a monster, and try to eavesdrop on the spirit's mumblings.
        ONCE_I_LEARN_OF_THESE_RAVINGS_I_WILL                                    = 10036,  -- Once I learn of these ravings, I will be able to carry out my role as an exorcist.
        WILL_YOU_HELP_OF_COURSE_NOT_A_GHOST                                     = 10037,  -- Will you help? Of course. Not a ghost of a chance.
        AHAHA_HOW_DROLL_PLEASE_SPEAK_WITH_ME_AGAIN                              = 10038,  -- Ahaha... How droll. Please speak with me again if you change your mind.
        MOST_EXCELLENT_THERE_IS_ONE_THING_YOU_MUST                              = 10039,  -- Most excellent. There is one thing you must be aware of, however.
        THESE_SPIRITS_WERE_ONCE_PEOPLE_SUCH_AS_YOU                              = 10040,  -- These spirits were once people such as you and I. If they see you directly, there is a good chance they will see through your disguise.
        IF_BY_CHANCE_YOUR_DISGUISE_FAILS_YOU_SIMPLY                             = 10041,  -- If, by chance, your disguise fails you, simply assume a monstrous form once again and continue your pursuit.
        I_AM_AWARE_OF_TWO_SPIRITS_THAT_HAUNT                                    = 10042,  -- I am aware of two spirits that haunt this town.
        THE_ONE_KNOWN_AS_GUWANANA_IS_THE_MOST                                   = 10043,  -- The one known as Guwanana is the most alert and suspicious, so I will ask you to first track down the Mithran spirit by the name of Bikho Ronpotteh.
        ONCE_YOU_HAVE_A_CLEAR_IDEA_OF_WHY                                       = 10044,  -- Once you have a clear idea of why the ghost has appeared here, I want you to report your findings to me immediately.
        GOOD_LUCK                                                               = 10045,  -- Good luck.
        IS_THAT_THE_GLOW_OF_SUCCESS_I_SEE                                       = 10046,  -- Is that the glow of success I see upon your face? What of the spirit...?
        I_SEE_SO_THAT_IS_HER_PURPOSE                                            = 10047,  -- I see... So that is her purpose...
        THE_TALE_IS_TRAGIC_BUT_THIS_WORLD_IS                                    = 10048,  -- The tale is tragic, but this world is no longer meant for one such as she.
        I_WILL_PREPARE_FOR_THE_EXORCISM                                         = 10049,  -- I will prepare for the exorcism.
        YOU_HAVE_BEEN_A_GREAT_HELP_PLEASE_TAKE                                  = 10050,  -- You have been a great help. Please take this as a token of my appreciation.
        THIS_IS_A_HAT_MODELED_AFTER_THOSE_WORN                                  = 10051,  -- This is a hat modeled after those worn by the Dark Lilies. Perhaps you might wear it during the season's festivities. Enjoy yourself, and forget about this sorrowful affair.
        HOWEVER_SHOULD_YOU_WISH_TO_AID_IN_ANOTHER                               = 10052,  -- However, should you wish to aid in another exorcism, I would welcome your help.
        WHAT_HAS_BEFALLEN_YOU_DO_YOU_WISH_TO                                    = 10053,  -- What has befallen you? Do you wish to give up?
        GIVE_UP_I_M_DONE_NOT_YET                                                = 10054,  -- Give up? I'm done. Not yet.
        A_PITY_PLEASE_SPEAK_WITH_ME_AGAIN_IF                                    = 10055,  -- A pity. Please speak with me again if you change your mind.
        THEN_PLEASE_RETURN_TO_YOUR_PURSUIT_OF_THE                               = 10056,  -- Then please return to your pursuit of the spirits.
        AH_YOU_RE_BACK_PERHAPS_YOU_HAVE_ENOUGH                                  = 10057,  -- Ah, you're back! Perhaps you have enough experience now to stalk the more alert ghost of the two.
        WILL_YOU_CONSENT_TO_AID_ME_AGAIN                                        = 10058,  -- Will you consent to aid me again?
        THE_SECOND_SPIRIT_IS_CALLED_GUWANANA_SHE_IS                             = 10059,  -- The second spirit is called Guwanana. She is well aware of her surroundings, so I urge the utmost care when following her.
        GOOD_DAY_I_SUPPOSE_YOU_VE_HEARD_OF                                      = 10060,  -- Good day! I suppose you've heard of all the ghost sightings around town?
        I_WOULDN_T_EXPECT_ANYTHING_LESS_FROM_AN                                 = 10061,  -- I wouldn't expect anything less from an adventurer.
        I_LL_GET_STRAIGHT_TO_THE_POINT_DO                                       = 10062,  -- I'll get straight to the point. Do you want to help in an exorcism?
        WELL_YOU_ADVENTURERS_ARE_PRETTY_BUSY_I_GUESS                            = 10063,  -- Well, you adventurers are pretty busy, I guess. Let me give you the short version:
        I_M_A_STRANGER_TO_THIS_LAND_CALLED                                      = 10064,  -- I'm a stranger to this land, called in by one of those important types.
        FOR_WHAT_I_HAPPEN_TO_HAVE_A_CERTAIN                                     = 10065,  -- For what? I happen to have a certain level of fame as an exorcist. You know--a banisher of spirits.
        BUT_THESE_SPIRITS_ARE_PROVING_TO_BE_A                                   = 10066,  -- But these spirits are proving to be a bit of a handful.
        THEY_WERE_POWERFUL_WITCHES_IN_LIFE_AND_USED                             = 10067,  -- They were powerful witches in life and used to belong to some famous coven.
        THE_WORST_THING_IS_THEY_USE_SOME_BEASTLY                                = 10068,  -- The worst thing is, they use some beastly language known as the Cursed Tongue. That's not a language I can understand.
        THAT_S_A_PROBLEM_BECAUSE_AS_AN_EXORCIST                                 = 10069,  -- That's a problem because, as an exorcist, I need to learn what's in their hearts and minds. Then I can find a weakness.
        THAT_S_WHERE_YOU_COME_IN                                                = 10070,  -- That's where you come in...
        I_NEED_YOU_TO_DISGUISE_YOURSELF_AS_A                                    = 10071,  -- I need you to disguise yourself as a monster and get close enough to find out what they're thinking.
        ONCE_I_KNOW_SOME_DETAILS_I_CAN_BEGIN                                    = 10072,  -- Once I know some details, I can begin the exorcism and rid this town of its unwelcome guests.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_SAY_WILL_YOU_HELP                                           = 10073,  -- What do you say? Will you help?
        OH_WELL_GHOSTS_AREN_T_EVERYBODY_S_CUP                                   = 10074,  -- Oh... Well, ghosts aren't everybody's cup of tea. I'll be here if you change your mind.
        THANK_YOU_THERE_IS_ONE_THING_YOU_SHOULD                                 = 10075,  -- Thank you! There is one thing you should know...
        THESE_GHOSTS_ARE_A_LITTLE_VAGUE_BUT_THEY                                = 10076,  -- These ghosts are a little vague, but they were once people too. If they get a good look at you, they'll know you're just wearing a costume...
        BUT_DON_T_GIVE_UP_IF_THEY_CATCH                                         = 10077,  -- But don't give up if they catch on to you. Just put the disguise back on and try again.
        I_VE_LOCATED_TWO_SPIRITS_FLOATING_AROUND_THIS                           = 10078,  -- I've located two spirits floating around this town.
        THE_FIRST_ONE_PRETTY_HEART_IS_FAIRLY_SHARP                              = 10079,  -- The first one, Pretty Heart, is fairly sharp. I suggest you go after Selma, the second spirit, to get your feet wet.
        ONCE_YOU_VE_FIGURED_OUT_WHY_THE_GHOST                                   = 10080,  -- Once you've figured out why the ghost is here, you need to tell me about it right away.
        GOOD_LUCK_2                                                             = 10081,  -- Good luck!
        OHO_LOOKS_LIKE_YOU_VE_MANAGED_TO_LEARN                                  = 10082,  -- Oho, looks like you've managed to learn something...
        HMMM_SO_THAT_S_WHY                                                      = 10083,  -- Hmmm... So that's why...
        IT_MIGHT_SEEM_CRUEL_BUT_THAT_GHOST_NO                                   = 10084,  -- It might seem cruel, but that ghost no longer belongs here. The exorcism is for their sake as much as ours...
        IT_S_TIME_TO_BEGIN_MY_PREPARATION                                       = 10085,  -- It's time to begin my preparation.
        OH_AND_THIS_IS_FOR_YOU                                                  = 10086,  -- Oh, and this is for you.
        IT_S_A_WITCH_HAT_THE_DESIGN_MATCHES                                     = 10087,  -- It's a witch hat. The design matches those worn by the coven I mentioned. Put it on, and go have fun. Forget about ghosts for a while.
        IF_YOU_WANT_TO_TRY_YOUR_HAND_AT                                         = 10088,  -- If you want to try your hand at ghost-chasing again, I'll be right here.
        GIVING_UP_THE_GHOST                                                     = 10089,  -- Giving up the ghost?
        OH_WELL_GHOSTS_AREN_T_EVERYBODY_S_CUP_2                                 = 10090,  -- Oh... Well, ghosts aren't everybody's cup of tea. I'll be here if you change your mind.
        THEN_IT_S_BACK_TO_CHASING_SPIRITS_WITH                                  = 10091,  -- Then it's back to chasing spirits with you!
        YOU_KNOW_WHAT_I_THINK_YOU_COULD_PROBABLY                                = 10092,  -- You know what? I think you could probably track that other ghost now that you have some experience.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_THINK                                                       = 10093,  -- What do you think?
        YOUR_TARGET_S_NAME_IS_PRETTY_HEART_WONDER                               = 10094,  -- Your target's name is Pretty Heart. Wonder why he's called that...
        REALLY_I_M_PRETTY_SURE_YOU_VE_GOT                                       = 10095,  -- Really? I'm pretty sure you've got it in you...
        HI_I_M_GERTRUDE_I_CAME_TO_INVESTIGATE                                   = 10096,  -- Hi, I'm Gertrude. I came to investigate the rumors of ghosts haunting this town. Have you heard anything?
        YOU_HAVE_WELL_THAT_MAKES_MY_JOB_EASIER                                  = 10097,  -- You have? Well, that makes my job easier, then.
        DO_YOU_THINK_YOU_COULD_HELP_OUT_A                                       = 10098,  -- Do you think you could help out a struggling exorcist?
        NO_THEN_LET_ME_FILL_YOU_IN_ON                                           = 10099,  -- No? Then let me fill you in on the details.
        I_MAY_NOT_APPEAR_AS_SUCH_BUT_I                                          = 10100,  -- I may not appear as such, but I'm actually an exorcist from a land far to the west.
        A_CERTAIN_PERSONAGE_FROM_THIS_NATION_SUMMONED_ME                        = 10101,  -- A certain personage from this nation summoned me to banish the spirits plaguing the city.
        BUT_ONCE_I_ARRIVED_I_DISCOVERED_THESE_GHOSTS                            = 10102,  -- But once I arrived, I discovered these ghosts were not your average apparitions.
        IN_LIFE_THEY_WERE_FEARSOME_WITCHES_AND_WIELDED                          = 10103,  -- In life, they were fearsome witches and wielded destructive spells of tremendous power.
        THEIR_STRENGTH_HAS_FOLLOWED_THEM_INTO_THE_AFTERLIFE                     = 10104,  -- Their strength has followed them into the afterlife, giving them a high level of resistance to my exorcisms.
        IN_THIS_SORT_OF_CASE_I_WOULD_USUALLY                                    = 10105,  -- In this sort of case, I would usually find some clue from their former lives in order to empower my rituals.
        THE_PROBLEM_IS_THESE_SPIRITS_SPEAK_THE_CURSED                           = 10106,  -- The problem is, these spirits speak the Cursed Tongue, and I can't understand enough of that language to learn anything.
        AND_SO_I_M_FORCED_TO_CALL_UPON                                          = 10107,  -- And so, I'm forced to call upon adventurers to aid me.
        WOULD_YOU_BE_WILLING_TO_DISGUISE_YOURSELF_AS                            = 10108,  -- Would you be willing to disguise yourself as a monster and try to discover what drives these beings?
        ADVENTURERS_ARE_OFTEN_VERY_BUSY_OR_SO_I                                 = 10109,  -- Adventurers are often very busy, or so I've heard. Please come back if you change your mind.
        WONDERFUL_THERE_IS_ONE_THING_I_MUST_WARN                                = 10110,  -- Wonderful. There is one thing I must warn you of, however.
        THESE_WITCHES_WERE_ONCE_PEOPLE_AND_ARE_CLEVER                           = 10111,  -- These witches were once people, and are clever enough to see through your disguise should you be too careless.
        IF_THEY_DO_HAPPEN_TO_FIND_YOU_OUT                                       = 10112,  -- If they do happen to find you out, please don't give up. They will soon forget, and you can don your costume once again.
        ACCORDING_TO_MY_SOURCES_THERE_ARE_TWO_GHOSTS                            = 10113,  -- According to my sources, there are two ghosts in this area.
        THE_ONE_CALLED_MARYSE_IS_EXTREMELY_VIGILANT_AND                         = 10114,  -- The one called Maryse is extremely vigilant and aware of her surroundings. I suggest you try following Poseaulloie first to get some practice.
        ONCE_YOU_VE_DISCOVERED_THE_GHOST_S_REASON                               = 10115,  -- Once you've discovered the ghost's reason for remaining in this world, please inform me at once. There are many preparations to be made.
        GOOD_LUCK_3                                                             = 10116,  -- Good luck!
        HOW_DID_YOU_FARE                                                        = 10117,  -- How did you fare...?
        I_SEE_SO_THAT_S_WHY_SHE                                                 = 10118,  -- I see, so that's why she...
        HOWEVER_IT_IS_MY_DUTY_TO_GIVE_HER                                       = 10119,  -- However, it is my duty to give her that little push she needs to leave this world behind.
        I_WILL_BEGIN_PREPARING_FOR_THE_EXORCISM                                 = 10120,  -- I will begin preparing for the exorcism.
        YOUR_HELP_HAS_BEEN_INVALUABLE_WOULD_YOU_ACCEPT                          = 10121,  -- Your help has been invaluable. Would you accept this in appreciation?
        IT_S_A_WITCH_HAT_PLEASE_WEAR_IT                                         = 10122,  -- It's a witch hat. Please wear it in the festivities and forget about ghosts and spirits for a while...
        IF_YOU_HAVE_TIME_I_WOULD_GLADLY_ACCEPT                                  = 10123,  -- If you have time, I would gladly accept your help again.
        WHAT_S_WRONG_HAVE_YOU_GROWN_TIRED_OF                                    = 10124,  -- What's wrong? Have you grown tired of your task?
        OH_I_SEE_WELL_PLEASE_RETURN_TO_ME                                       = 10125,  -- Oh, I see... Well, please return to me if you find your patience for this task restored.
        THEN_I_WOULD_ASK_YOU_TO_RETURN_TO                                       = 10126,  -- Then I would ask you to return to your task. Good luck.
        WOULD_YOU_CONSIDER_AN_ATTEMPT_AT_FOLLOWING_THE                          = 10127,  -- Would you consider an attempt at following the more wily of the two spirits?
        I_M_SURE_YOU_HAVE_SUFFICIENT_EXPERIENCE_NOW                             = 10128,  -- I'm sure you have sufficient experience now.
        THEN_YOUR_NEXT_TARGET_IS_THE_ONE_KNOWN                                  = 10129,  -- Then your next target is the one known as Maryse. Please be careful...
        YOU_MUST_RECOVER_YOUR_STRENGTH_BEFORE_YOU_CONTINUE                      = 10130,  -- You must recover your strength before you continue pursuing these supernatural intruders. Return to me once you have had time to rest.
        I_APPRECIATE_THE_OFFER_OF_HELP_BUT_YOU                                  = 10131,  -- I appreciate the offer of help, but you're in no state to be chasing ghosts. Build your strength, rest your mind, and return to me when you're ready.
        I_M_HAPPY_TO_HAVE_SOMEONE_SO_COOPERATIVE                                = 10132,  -- I'm happy to have someone so cooperative on my side, but too much contact with spirits will drain your strength. Return to me on the morrow when you've had time to rest.
        YOU_YOU_RE_NO_MONSTER                                                   = 10133,  -- !!! You...you're no monster!
        YOU_YOU_RE_NO_MONSTER_2                                                 = 10134,  -- !!! You...you're no monster!
        YOU_YOU_RE_NO_MONSTER_3                                                 = 10135,  -- !!! You...you're no monster!
        YOU_YOU_RE_NO_MONSTER_4                                                 = 10136,  -- !!! You...you're no monster!
        SO_PRETTY_THE_FOUNTAIN_IS_STILL_SO                                      = 10137,  -- So pretty...the fountain is still so...
        THAT_MUST_BE_THE_CHATEAU_AND_OVER_THERE                                 = 10138,  -- That must be...the chateau... And over there...the cathedral...
        I_NEVER_THOUGHT_TO_RETURN_HERE                                          = 10139,  -- I never thought...to return here...
        EVERY_MORNING_I_WATCHED_HIM_TRAINING_FROM_AFAR                          = 10140,  -- Every morning...I watched him training...from afar... If only...I had had the courage...
        NO_HE_WAS_A_HUME_I_AM_A                                                 = 10141,  -- No...he was a Hume... I...am a witch... If I were...to confess...
        AND_THEN_THERE_WAS_THE_LUNCH_HE_ALWAYS                                  = 10142,  -- And then...there was the lunch...he always carried... Someone...must have made it...for him...
        HE_PASSED_WITHOUT_EVER_KNOWING_BUT_I_AM                                 = 10143,  -- He passed...without ever knowing... But I...am still here...
        I_I_SHOULD_NO_LONGER_CARE_I_WANT                                        = 10144,  -- I... I should no longer care... I want to forget...
        THE_FOUNTAIN_WHERE_HE_TOOK_HIS_REST_THE                                 = 10145,  -- The fountain where he took his rest... The stones that grew wet with his tears... Nothing has changed...except me...
        THE_MOAT_WHERE_HE_SWAM_THE_SHADE_WHERE                                  = 10146,  -- The moat where he swam... The shade where he slept... It is still the same...
        AH_I_KNOW_YOU_ARE_THERE_BUT_TO                                          = 10147,  -- Ah...I know you are there... But to have someone hear my pain...has lightened my soul...if only a little...
        THIS_MOAT_WHERE_I_FELL_IN                                               = 10148,  -- This moat...where I fell in...
        I_SLIPPED_ON_THE_BRIDGE_I_FELL                                          = 10149,  -- I slipped...on the bridge... I fell...
        HE_WAS_ALWAYS_THERE_I_DIDN_T_NOTICE                                     = 10150,  -- He was always there... I didn't notice...
        FROM_THE_TIME_THAT_I_WAS_SMALL_ALWAYS                                   = 10151,  -- From the time that I was small... Always there to save me...
        EVEN_WHEN_I_WAS_LOATHED_AND_FEARED_YOU                                  = 10152,  -- Even when I was loathed and feared... You were there to praise my power...
        MY_BROTHER                                                              = 10153,  -- My brother...
        BUT_I_I_WAS_ALWAYS_ANGRY_I_EVEN                                         = 10154,  -- But I...I was always angry... I even forgot the lunch you made...
        BUT_HERE_I_WANT_TO_TELL_YOU_JUST                                        = 10155,  -- But here... I want to tell you just once...
        THANK_YOU_THANK_YOU_FOR_BEING_THERE_FOR                                 = 10156,  -- Thank you... Thank you for being there...for me...
        YOUR_LUNCHES_ALWAYS_MADE_WITH_SO_MUCH_CARE                              = 10157,  -- Your lunches...always made with so much care...
        I_SEE_YOU_THERE_LISTENING_TO_ME_I                                       = 10158,  -- I see you there... Listening to me... I should curse you... But I will forgive you...as my brother would...
        THESE_TREES_I_BURNED_WITH_THE_FIRE_SPELL                                = 10159,  -- These trees... I burned with the Fire spell... Yet they have grown back...
        THIS_STREAM_I_FROZE_WITH_BLIZZAGA_II_YET                                = 10160,  -- This stream... I froze with Blizzaga II... Yet now it flows...
        THIS_BUILDING_I_TOPPLED_WITH_AEROGA_III_YET                             = 10161,  -- This building... I toppled with Aeroga III... Yet it has been rebuilt...
        THE_WALL_OF_THE_METALWORKS_I_CRACKED_WITH                               = 10162,  -- The wall of the Metalworks... I cracked with Thunder IV... Yet it has been repaired...
        IT_IS_AS_IF_I_NEVER_EXISTED_HAVE                                        = 10163,  -- It is as if...I never existed... Have my sins...also been erased...?
        MY_MAGIC_HAS_ALWAYS_BEEN_OVERPOWERFUL_THE_COLD                          = 10164,  -- My magic...has always been overpowerful... The cold stares...of the townspeople...
        I_LEARNED_MY_SPELLS_FOR_VENGEANCE_PEOPLE_CALLED                         = 10165,  -- I learned my spells...for vengeance... People called me...heartless...
        I_LOATHED_THIS_NATION_THIS_TOWN_ITS_PEOPLE                              = 10166,  -- I loathed...this nation...this town...its people...
        THEN_WHY_WHY_DO_I_FEEL_SO_AT                                            = 10167,  -- Then why...? Why do I feel so at home here...?
        WHY_WHY_DOES_EVERYTHING_FEEL_SO_DEAR_TO                                 = 10168,  -- Why...? Why does everything feel...so dear to me...?
        YOU_I_SEE_YOU_CEASE_YOUR_STALKING_I                                     = 10169,  -- You...I see you... Cease your stalking... I wish to be alone...
        A_GENIUS_IS_NEVER_UNDERSTOOD_BY_THE_MASSES                              = 10170,  -- A genius...is never understood...by the masses...
        A_GENIUS_IS_ISOLATED_FROM_THE_COMMON_PEOPLE                             = 10171,  -- A genius...is isolated...from the common people...
        A_GENIUS_WILL_BE_PERSECUTED_BY_THOSE_WHO                                = 10172,  -- A genius...will be persecuted...by those who do not understand...
        I_WANTED_TO_SAVE_HER_THE_GIRL_WITH                                      = 10173,  -- I wanted to save her... The girl with astounding talent...
        TO_HELP_THE_GIRL_WHO_HAD_NOTHING_BUT                                    = 10174,  -- To help...the girl...who had nothing but her magic...
        THE_DARK_LILIES_A_COVEN_OF_CHOSEN_A                                     = 10175,  -- The Dark Lilies... A coven of...chosen... A sanctuary...for witches...
        YET_I_WONDER_WAS_IT_ALL_FOR_THE                                         = 10176,  -- Yet...I wonder... Was it all...for the best...? To leave...this world behind...?
        WAS_SHE_TRULY_HAPPY_BEING_ENVELOPED_IN_THE                              = 10177,  -- Was she...truly happy...? Being enveloped...in the darkness...?
        I_WANTED_TO_SEARCH_FOR_THE_ANSWERS_ONE                                  = 10178,  -- I wanted to search...for the answers...one more time... In this town...the town I had forsaken...
        I_WISHED_TO_GAZE_ONCE_MORE_ON_THE                                       = 10179,  -- I wished to gaze once more...on the answers to be found... In this town...that I once loved...
        YOU_GO_BACK_BACK_TO_THE_EXORCIST_TELL                                   = 10180,  -- You...go back... Back to the exorcist... Tell him...I am ready...to leave...
        THIS_WAS_A_SECRET_PLACE                                                 = 10181,  -- This...was a secret place...
        A_PLACE_THAT_NOBODY_KNEW                                                = 10182,  -- A place...that nobody knew...
        THE_PERRRFECT_SPOT                                                      = 10183,  -- The perrrfect spot...
        AN_ENCHANTED_SPOT_SO_MANY_FISH_THEY_WOULD                               = 10184,  -- An enchanted spot... So many fish... They would just jump...onto the hook...
