        REMEMBER_YOU_WILL_NOT_BE_ABLE_TO_USE                                    = 11750,  -- Remember, you will not be able to use any chocobucks earned in [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst] here, and you will also lose any Solo Victory Points that you may have. Are you sure you want to go through with this?
        JOIN_THIS_TEAM_YES_NO                                                   = 11751,  -- Join this team? Yes. No.
