        VIEW_WHICH_RECIPE_P_NONE_RETURN_TO_PAGE                                 = 13057,  -- View which recipe? ([Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran], p. #). None. %. %. %. %. %. %. %. %. Return to page selection. Previous page. Next page.
        OH_THE_WHY_THAT_S_ONE_OF_MY                                             = 13058,  -- Oh, the %? Why, that's one of my favorite recipes, too! What skills does it require? Let's see here...
